<template>
  <v-form
    ref="form"
  >
    <v-text-field
    :value="$store.state.exibicaoDoObjeto.objeto.live"    
    label="Live"
    outlined
    :readonly="$store.state.exibicaoDoObjeto.modoEdicao"
    ></v-text-field>

    <v-text-field
    v-model="$store.state.exibicaoDoObjeto.objeto.palestrante"
    label="Palestrante"
    outlined
    :readonly="$store.state.exibicaoDoObjeto.modoEdicao"
    ></v-text-field>

    <v-text-field
    v-model="$store.state.exibicaoDoObjeto.objeto.descricao"
    label="Descrição"
    outlined
    :readonly="$store.state.exibicaoDoObjeto.modoEdicao"
    ></v-text-field>

    <v-text-field
    v-model="$store.state.exibicaoDoObjeto.objeto.empresa"
    :counter="10"
    label="Empresa"
    outlined
    :readonly="$store.state.exibicaoDoObjeto.modoEdicao"
    ></v-text-field>

    <v-date-picker v-model="picker"></v-date-picker>

    
  </v-form>
</template>

<script>
  export default {
    data () {
      return {
        picker: (new Date(Date.now() - (new Date()).getTimezoneOffset() * 60000)).toISOString().substr(0, 10),
      }
    },
  }
</script>

<style>

</style>
